Dec 16, 2001

xqf-0.9.8.tar.gz created using:

Mandrake 8
libtool 1.4
gettext 0.10.40

tar.gz:

-fresh cvs checkout
-update version in NEWS, configure.in, docs/xqfdocs.html, ChangeLog
-touch xqf/ltconfig
-./autogen.sh
-./configure
-./make dist

